text: Kettle Creek is a stream in Caldwell and Daviess County in the U.S. state of Missouri. According to tradition, Kettle Creek was named on account of a party leaving a kettle along its course. ==See also== *List of rivers of Missouri ==References== Category:Rivers of Caldwell County, Missouri Category:Rivers of Daviess County, Missouri Category:Rivers of Missouri
title: Kettle Creek (Missouri)
